data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bed, 2-bath home with a 3-car garage. This spacious residence boasts an impressive design. As you enter, you'll immediately notice the grandeur of the cathedral ceiling, adding an airy and open ambiance to the living space. Complete with a master suite, you'll enjoy the privacy and convenience of a large bathroom and a convenient walk-through to the laundry area. This thoughtful layout ensures ease and efficiency in your daily routines. This property boasts a 3-car garage, providing abundant space for vehicle storage, hobbies, or a workshop. Whether you have multiple cars or enjoy indulging in DIY projects, the garage is designed to meet your needs. **Seller is offering concessions towards buyer's rate buy down and/ or closing costs. **
